Check the Pets.ie database table to find similar concepts to reduce later work.
These would be the columns of the pet table. 

I will continue to use the mtcdb1 database and add the pet table.

Use a sql table dump to edit the contents.

CREATE TABLE pet
(
	petID char(10) not null	PRIMARY KEY,
	petType varchar(50) not null,
	petAddress1 varchar(100) not null,
	petAddress2 varchar(100) null,
	petCity varchar(100) null,
	petCounty varchar(100) not null,
	petEmail varchar(100) null,
	petPhoneNo varchar(100) null,
	petImageSource varchar(100) null
);
